Changes for the Labyrinth-Plugin-Requests
=========================================

1.05	2015-01-24
        - extended META test suite.

1.04	2014-12-27
        - fixed license fields in META.json to be lists.
        - added homepage resource to META files.

1.03	2014-07-14
        - Exporter tag ':default in Labyrinth::Globals no longer used.
        - now require Labyrinth-5.22.

1.02	2014-04-26
        - fixed distribution name in META.
        - added LICENSE file.

1.01	2013-03-30
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
        - added minimum perl version (5.006).
        - reworked Makefile.PL for clarity.
        - upgraded to Test::CPAN::Meta::JSON for tests.
        - test suite update.

1.00	2011-01-20
        - first official release
